Request proper citation for biography detail that relies only on the subject's own press releases and updating description of subject to reflect the description given in all newspaper reports

From review of this article it is clear that a major contributor is connected to the subject. The original content all relies on dead links and the subject's own websites, whilst any properly sourced material posted by editors is being removed by someone monitoring the page. This page needs a complete review.
